Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:19.19,Main03,ENDING CREDITPREVIEWITO,0,0,0,,I didn't expect anything\Nlike that, Okita-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.53,0:24:24.33,Main03,ENDING CREDITPREVIEWITO,0,0,0,,That you would be on my\Nside. What do you desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.68,0:24:28.05,Main03,OKITA,0,0,0,,Naturally…the Vice-Chief position.
